data.description: Prepare to be amazed by this spectacular basement ranch-style property! Featuring three beds and two baths, it offers ample space for a family to grow and thrive. Step outside onto the deck or screened-in porch, and you'll be greeted by a spacious, fenced-in backyard, perfect for entertaining and making memories with your loved ones. The kitchen and bathrooms have been updated with modern finishes, and new flooring, paint, doors, trim, and lights have been added throughout the property, bringing a fresh and inviting feel to every room. You'll also be delighted to find a wonderful playground and above-ground pool in the backyard, perfect for endless days of fun and relaxation. Plus, the oversized garage can easily accommodate two cars, with extra space for storage or a workshop. Located in a well-established neighborhood, this residence ensures a peaceful ambiance while still being just minutes away from the conveniences of West Knoxville.
